System Installation scripts
===========================

Installation
------------

Install packages, including pkgs in rep o(pacman, yaourt) 

partition disks

format partition

mount root partition

install base group pkgs

pacstrap /mnt base

generate fstab
genfstab -U -p /mnt >> /mnt/etc/fstab

add repo of archlinuxfr to pacman config

config mirrorlist of pacman to 163 and sohu

chroot to /mnt
arch-root /mnt
pacman -S xorg-server xorg-xinit xorg-utils xorg-server-utils mesa
pacman -S xf86-video-vesa xf86-video-intel
pacman -S syslinux
syslinux-install_update -i -a -m

execute pacman pkg install functions

add user dongkc

set passwd for dongkc

config sudo configs for dongkc


Configuration
-------------

config syslinux

configuration, both systemwide and userwide
